text: Upper Orakzai is a tehsil of Orakzai District in the Khyber Pakhtunkhwa province of Pakistan. Some of main areas of Upper Orakzai include: * Dabori * Kool * Badan * Zanka khel * Zakhtan * Spaidar ali khel * Chapar ali khel * Sam Mamoozi * Arghunja * Mir kalam khel * Stara kada * Swaro kot * Ghuljo * Kandi Mishti * Takhtak * Khwaga seri/sarka * Narek * Yakh kandow *Gandi tal *Tari mela *Sara khawa *Gall Category:Tehsils of Khyber Pakhtunkhwa
title: Upper Orakzai Tehsil
